# Todone Architecture Documentation

## Overview
This document provides comprehensive architecture documentation for the Todone application system design.

## System Architecture

### Frontend
- React with TypeScript
- Vite build system
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- React Router for navigation

### Backend
- Node.js with Express
- RESTful API design
- JWT authentication
- MongoDB database

### State Management
- Zustand for client-side state
- Context API for component communication
- Custom hooks for business logic

## Data Flow

1. User interacts with UI components
2. Components dispatch actions to services
3. Services make API calls to backend
4. Backend processes requests and returns data
5. Data is stored in state management
6. UI components react to state changes

## Component Hierarchy

```
App
├── AuthProvider
├── TaskProvider
├── ProjectProvider
├── UI Components
└── Pages